title: Essential Pixies Collection 2009
description:
Want a good quality collection of the Pixies best work without having to download and sort through their entire discography? If so, this torrent is for you!

There are 28 songs in this torrent (see file list for tracks included). All are MP3 based and most are Variable Bit Rate (VBR) encoded. These will play perfectly in iTunes or any other MP3 compatible player. All are properly tagged and file named and include album artwork embedded right inside the tag itself.

Enjoy!
